{"name": "extractous", "metadata": {"name": "extractous", "version": "0.2.0", "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: CPython", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: PyPy", "Programming Language :: Rust"], "home_page": "https://extractous.yobix.ai/", "license": "Apache-2.0", "documentation_url": "https://extractous.yobix.ai/docs/python/index.html", "dependencies": [], "summary": "Extractous Python Binding", "upload_time": 1731886656}, "documentation": ["# Extractous Python Bindings\n\nThis project provides Python bindings for the Extractous library, allowing you to use extractous functionality in\nyour Python applications.\n\n## Installation\n\nTo install the extractous Python bindings, you can use pip:\n\n```bash\npip install extractous\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nExtracting a file to string:\n\n```python\nfrom extractous import Extractor\n\n# Create a new extractor\nextractor = Extractor()\nextractor.set_extract_string_max_length(1000)\n\n# Extract text from a file\nresult, metadata = extractor.extract_file_to_string(\"README.md\")\nprint(result)\nprint(metadata)\n```\n\nExtracting a file(URL / bytearray) to a buffered stream:\n\n```python\nfrom extractous import Extractor\n\nextractor = Extractor()\n# for file\nreader, metadata = extractor.extract_file(\"tests/quarkus.pdf\")\n# for url\n# reader, metadata = extractor.extract_url(\"https://www.google.com\")\n# for bytearray\n# with open(\"tests/quarkus.pdf\", \"rb\") as file:\n#     buffer = bytearray(file.read())\n# reader, metadata = extractor.extract_bytes(buffer)\n\nresult = \"\"\nbuffer = reader.read(4096)\nwhile len(buffer) > 0:\n    result += buffer.decode(\"utf-8\")\n    buffer = reader.read(4096)\n\nprint(result)\nprint(metadata)\n```\n\nExtracting a file with OCR:\n\n```python\nfrom extractous import Extractor, TesseractOcrConfig\n\nextractor = Extractor().set_ocr_config(TesseractOcrConfig().set_language(\"deu\"))\nresult, metadata = extractor.extract_file_to_string(\"../../test_files/documents/eng-ocr.pdf\")\n\nprint(result)\nprint(metadata)\n```\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "python.extractous", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "python.extractous.libpath", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "python.extractous.__doc__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "python.extractous.system", "xref": {"fqname": "platform.system", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "bindings.extractous-python.python.extractous", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "bindings.extractous-python.python.extractous.libpath", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bindings.extractous-python.python.extractous.__doc__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "bindings.extractous-python.python.extractous.system", "xref": {"fqname": "platform.system", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "bindings.extractous-python.tests.test_pdf", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "bindings.extractous-python.tests.test_pdf.expected_result", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bindings.extractous-python.tests.test_pdf.test_extract_file_to_string", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bindings.extractous-python.tests.test_pdf.test_extract_file", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bindings.extractous-python.tests.test_pdf.test_extract_bytes", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "bindings.extractous-python.tests.test_extract_url", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "bindings.extractous-python.tests.test_extract_url.test_extract_url_to_stream", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bindings.extractous-python.tests.test_extract_url.test_extract_url_to_str